//This file contains hardware structure for robot & computers

Arlo Robot
  -ActivityBoard
  -Wheels/Motors
  -Encoders
  -HB-25 Motor Encoders ( turn servo/Parallax pulses into motor pulses )

Computer ( On top of Arlo robot )
  -Camera ( Connected to computer )
  -Internet Connection ( Required )
  
Computer ( Remote Connection )
  -Camera ( Connected to computer )
  -Internet Connection ( Required )
